    <item>
      <title>太空总监说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-satellites-risk-attack-in-a-war-with-china-space-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京在太空中的野心构成了“令人难以置信的威胁”，以卫星为目标，是美国太空部队负责人周四在美国和中国之间的任何冲突中首先被击落的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-satellites-risk-attack-in-a-war-with-china-space-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sheinbaum将贸易局长派往华盛顿进行关税会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/sheinbaum-dispatches-trade-chief-to-washington-for-tariff-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥计划继续与美国就钢铁和自动关税进行谈判，即使与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）抨击的其他国家相比，克劳迪娅·辛巴姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）总统的政府庆祝其优惠待遇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/sheinbaum-dispatches-trade-chief-to-washington-for-tariff-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国的马克龙敦促欧盟公司暂停美国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-s-macron-urges-companies-to-pause-us-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）敦促公司在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布对欧洲联盟和其他地区的关税之后暂停在美国的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-s-macron-urges-companies-to-pause-us-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 14:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥说，我们不会退出北约推动国防支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马可·鲁比奥（Marco Rubio）坚持认为，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府无意离开北约，即使美国特使要求军事联盟成员棘手支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于世界上最贫穷的国家来说，特朗普关税是一场“灾难”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的新互惠关税将遭受世界上最贫穷的国家的最难打击，这使他们的劳动密集型出口行业处于危险之中，并降低了美国比竞争对手中国最大的经济优势之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非联盟teeters作为预算显示裂谷的扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-africa-s-coalition-teeters-as-budget-shows-widening-rift</link>
